---
title: Creamy Parmesan Chicken Spaghetti with Roasted Tomato & Basil
description: Our chefs just took pasta night to the next level: Thanks to spaghetti, tomatoes, and chicken with Tuscan herbs, this recipe has all the Italian flair you could want and then some. The dish is accompanied by a sauce that has all the creamy goodness you want—it’s got cream cheese, Parmesan, and butter for a trifecta of dairy deliciousness. So get ready—these tasty noodles are waiting to get twirled ‘round your fork.

